id=theettam_trip
name=Theettam Trip Mode
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=Mohithash
description=Blocks the modem data-path wakelocks while the screen is off, using the Boeffla wakelock blocker built into Theettam Kernel. Calls, SMS and alarms are untouched. Requires a kernel with CONFIG_BOEFFLA_WL_BLOCKER.
